## Unit 2 Day 4-6: 

First, let's explore the lesson in the curriculum. To begin, find your ECS Version 5 curriculum and open to page 81.

<a href="http://code.org/ecs#page=81" target="_blank">Access a Digital Copy of the Lesson >></a>

